{"tid":627541,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地手機殼驗出有毒致癌物　香港官網都買到","createTime":"2018-04-13T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T08:47:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"48d9d8342037642e028aa2ad7082f852f8673e4a","tid":627541,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"深圳消委會周四（12日）公布手機保護套檢測報告，抽查市面上28個熱門品牌共30款手機殼，其中5款被驗出含有毒或致癌物，更有一款的鉛含量更超標1550倍，長期接觸會直接傷害人體腦細胞、破壞骨骼，引發腎衰竭，更可能影響女性生育。在檢測的部分手機殼中，在香港也能買到。<br />\n<br />\n深圳消委會今次測試主要針對化學安全問題，在結合實際使用情況後，以歐盟、德國、美國等多地的標準作為化學測試指標。經檢測後，其中13款的手機殼表現優異，品質超出國際一流標準，在201項化學測試中均沒有被驗出含有毒有害化學物質，且經48小時的老化測試後，顯示其相當耐用，不易發黃變色。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，蘋果、小米等大品牌的5款手機殼，不但被驗出含有毒有害物質，如有多環芬烴、塑化劑、鉛、短鏈氯化石蠟等，且含量均超出標準，當中蘋果品牌型號為MR672FE/A的手機殼，官網售價288元（約360港元），為30款樣品中最貴的產品。另涉事的手機殼在香港官網也有發售，例如在蘋果官網輸入「MR672FE/A」，便會得出售價258港元的「iPhone8 / 7矽膠護殼 - 耀目黃色」，在小米香港官網搜索，也能得到同款的機殼出售。<br />\n<br />\n不過在眾多問題手機殼中，情況最嚴重的是一款躍寧的「水鑽閃粉彩膜」手機殼，不但含有上述所有有毒有害物質，鉛含量更達155000ppm，超過標準限值1550倍。<br />\n<br />\n消委會表示，現時全中國共有10.65億個手機殼用戶，佔手機用戶數量超過7成半，提醒手機殼可能含有毒有害物質，用戶切勿將之放入口。透明材質的手機殼容易發黃變色，但相對會較安全。最危險的是閃粉水鑽類的手機殼，「愈漂亮的手機殼可能愈有毒！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/131031_6d94f7ca63806f20eb8a0b13c4025a9b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F131031_6d94f7ca63806f20eb8a0b13c4025a9b.png&h=2fd0de44&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/13/131033_3a2297e7236f757b2a7cfe481700deef.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F13%2F131033_3a2297e7236f757b2a7cfe481700deef.png&h=ebd54504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/mobile/bkncn-20180413000059838-0413_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180413%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180413000059838-0413_05011_001.html&d=PIP6CtNqzdV40iPEgTS2v%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=e0ea0f33\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180413/mobile/bkncn-20180413000059838-0413_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"74b749299ff4320e2380120cacd4674cb213e705","tid":627541,"uid":119066,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"仆街用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12da58dbdb165cfb2e4244ec3499940030cae35c","tid":627541,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"無致癌先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd4f55c28a2583af5df2a82b3fca4150a7b487b4","tid":627541,"uid":46835,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:22:44.000Z","msg":"都係裸跑最實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d40360bb94596c019d7bdb49a8ac5f1d18d301","tid":627541,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T06:32:27.000Z","msg":"又害人我屌你老母"},{"pid":"9035b12bcde44838b2869aa238419a42fe61248e","tid":627541,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12da58dbdb165cfb2e4244ec3499940030cae35c","tid":627541,"uid":2267,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"無致癌先係新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:44:14.000Z","msg":"x2"},{"pid":"bc31dfe3749974168d67996bbcbaeac4c64ce1f5","tid":627541,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <